OL,3,CHero teacher has sleepless nights
OL,4,Cafter disarming Ammanford school
OL,5,Cstabber
OL,7,FDarrel Campbell was patrolling the
OL,8,Fyard at Ysgol Dyffryn Aman in
OL,9,FAmmanford, Carmarthenshire, last April
OL,10,Fwhen the then 13-year-old girl
OL,11,Flaunched a terrifying attack with a
OL,12,Fmulti-tool knife she had smuggled into
OL,13,Fschool.
OL,15,FTeacher Elizabeth Hopkin was airlifted
OL,16,Ffrom the school after being stabbed in
OL,17,Fthe neck, while her colleague Fiona
OL,18,FElias suffered stab wounds to her arms
OL,19,Fand hands and was also rushed to
OL,20,Fhospital.
