OL,4,Cafter disarming Ammanford school
OL,5,Cstabber
OL,7,FA female pupil was attacked and
OL,8,Fstabbed in the shoulder as staff at
OL,9,Fthe school struggled to contain the
OL,10,Fperpetrator.
OL,12,FAll three survived their injuries.
OL,14,FClose to 1,500 pupils were locked down
OL,15,Fin their classrooms as the girl was
OL,16,Fled away from the scene, while
OL,17,Fhundreds of concerned parents gathered
OL,18,Fat the school perimeter, desperate for
OL,19,Finformation.
