OL,3,CHero teacher has sleepless nights
OL,4,Cafter disarming Ammanford school
OL,5,Cstabber
OL,7,FDuring the criminal trial which
OL,8,Ffollowed, CCTV footage showed Mr
OL,9,FCampbell placing the girl in a
OL,10,Fheadlock and wrestling the knife from
OL,11,Fher grasp.
OL,13,FThe teacher, who has worked at the
OL,14,Fschool for more than 40 years, told
OL,15,FITV Wales how he acted on instinct as
OL,16,Fsoon as he became aware the girl was
OL,17,Fwielding a knife.
OL,19,F"Her hair was ruffled, she looked very
OL,20,Fangry, and she was just staring," he
OL,21,Ftold ITV News.
