OL,5,Cstabber
OL,7,F"We tried to calm her down, but she
OL,8,Fwalked away from us, so I followed
OL,9,Fher. She turned and looked across at
OL,10,Fanother group of pupils and let out a
OL,11,Fhorrific scream, and started running
OL,12,Ftowards them. It was at that point
OL,13,Fthat I saw the knife in her hand.
OL,15,F"I sprinted after her and managed to
OL,16,Fgrab her hand with the knife and put
OL,17,Fher into a headlock and restrain her
OL,18,Funtil further help came.
