OL,7,F"I had to act, and I had to do
OL,8,Fsomething to stop her from inflicting
OL,9,Fmore injuries. Everything else around
OL,10,Fme was a blur, I was just focusing on
OL,11,Fher."
OL,13,FIn February this year, a jury found
OL,14,Fthe teenage girl, now aged 14, guilty
OL,15,Fof the attempted murder of Ms Elias,
OL,16,FMs Hopkin and a fellow pupil.
