OL,3,CHero teacher has sleepless nights
OL,4,Cafter disarming Ammanford school
OL,5,Cstabber
OL,7,FMr Campbell admits the knife attack
OL,8,Fhas had an impact on his mental health
OL,9,Fand says trips away to the family's
OL,10,Fholiday home in Aberaeron have helped
OL,11,Fhim to take his mind off that day.
OL,13,F"I've had quite a few sleepless nights
OL,14,Fbecause of it," he said.
OL,16,F"I'm very lucky that I do have
OL,17,FAberaeron to escape to. I have found
OL,18,Fit very comforting to be able to come
OL,19,Fhere on most of our weekends to relax
OL,20,Fand be away from the hustle and bustle
OL,21,Fof Ammanford."
