OL,7,F"I feel sorry for the girl, in that
OL,8,Fshe has probably ruined her life," he
OL,9,Fadmits.
OL,11,F"But I also feel that for the future
OL,12,Fof education and the profession, she
OL,13,Fpossibly has to be made an example of.
OL,15,F"There is no easy answer to the
OL,16,Fproblem of school violence, but the
OL,17,FWelsh Government, the education
OL,18,Fauthorities and headteachers need to
OL,19,Fcome together to thrash things out.
